OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779440815
OL,3,CCheaper tickets for summer attractions
OL,4,Cand kids meals as Reeves slashes VAT
OL,6,FFamilies will get cheaper tickets for
OL,7,Ftheme parks and money off kids' meals
OL,8,Fout after the Chancellor announced she
OL,9,Fwas temporarily cutting VAT for summer
OL,10,Fattractions.
OL,12,FRachel Reeves revealed a detailed
OL,13,Fpackage of measures on Thursday
OL,14,Fdesigned to protect families from the
OL,15,Fcost-of-living squeeze triggered by
OL,16,Fthe war in Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779440815
OL,3,CCheaper tickets for summer attractions
OL,4,Cand kids meals as Reeves slashes VAT
OL,6,FThe plan will cut VAT from 20% to 5%
OL,7,Fon ticket prices for both adults and
OL,8,Fchildren for attractions such as
OL,9,Ffairs, theme parks, zoos and museums,
OL,10,Fas well as on children's tickets for
OL,11,Fcinemas, concerts, soft play, theatre
OL,12,Fand meals in restaurants and cafes.
OL,14,FThe Chancellor has called the raft of
OL,15,Fmeasures the 'Great British Summer
OL,16,FSavings Scheme', also announcing she
OL,17,Fwill increase tax-free mileage rates
OL,18,Fby 10p per mile, backdated to April
OL,19,F2026.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779440815
OL,3,CCheaper tickets for summer attractions
OL,4,Cand kids meals as Reeves slashes VAT
OL,6,FShe told the Commons: "I recognise
OL,7,Fthat what matters for families is not
OL,8,Fjust getting by but being able to
OL,9,Fenjoy time together without worrying
OL,10,Fabout the next bill. That is why I am
OL,11,Flaunching the Great British Summer
OL,12,FSavings scheme to help families and
OL,13,Fsupport our hospitality sector."
OL,15,FThe Chancellor said she would pay for
OL,16,Fcost-of-living support by changing how
OL,17,Foil and gas companies with overseas
OL,18,Foperations are taxed.
OL,26,@nD@WOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779440815
OL,3,CCheaper tickets for summer attractions
OL,4,Cand kids meals as Reeves slashes VAT
OL,6,FThis would put an end to the practice
OL,7,Fof some oil and gas groups structuring
OL,8,Ftheir tax affairs "in a way which
OL,9,Fensures they pay little or no
OL,10,Fcorporation tax on their UK energy
OL,11,Ftrading profits" and "raise hundreds
OL,12,Fof millions of pounds a year", Reeves
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,FThe Treasury said the scheme is
OL,16,Festimated to cost around #300 million,
OL,17,Fwith final costings detailed at the
OL,18,Fnext Budget.
OL,26,@pD@SOUsD@PO]sD@VOUtD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779440815
OL,3,CCheaper tickets for summer attractions
OL,4,Cand kids meals as Reeves slashes VAT
OL,6,FReeves also revealed a #350 million
OL,7,Fcritical chemicals resilience fund and
OL,8,Fa #120 million fund to help the
OL,9,Fceramics sector as part of cost-of-
OL,10,Fliving measures.
OL,12,FThe government has also announced free
OL,13,Fsummer bus rides for kids and possible
OL,14,Freductions on some food tariffs.
OL,16,FImport tariffs on more than 100 types
OL,17,Fof products will be cut in a move that
OL,18,Fis expected to save consumers more
OL,19,Fthan #150 million a year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779440815
OL,3,CCheaper tickets for summer attractions
OL,4,Cand kids meals as Reeves slashes VAT
OL,6,FThe full list of products will be
OL,7,Fpublished next week, but is expected
OL,8,Fto include biscuits, chocolate, dried
OL,9,Ffruit and nuts.
OL,11,FThe Treasury said the tariff
OL,12,Fsuspension is expected to save the
OL,13,Faverage household 10p off the weekly
OL,14,Fshop, which is around #5.20 per
OL,15,Fhousehold per year.
OL,17,FThe free bus travel scheme will allow
OL,18,Fevery child aged five to 15 in England
OL,19,Fto travel on participating local
OL,20,Froutes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
