PN,31407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779440815
OL,3,CCheaper tickets for summer attractions
OL,4,Cand kids meals as Reeves slashes VAT
OL,6,FThe chancellor is committing more than
OL,7,F#100 million to fund the free fares
OL,8,Fscheme and to support bus services
OL,9,Ffacing increased costs.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FThe Chancellor told MPs: "I know the
OL,17,Fcost of the weekly shop is often one
OL,18,Fof the biggest worries for families,
OL,19,Fso last month I met with supermarkets
OL,20,Fto urge them to do all they can to
OL,21,Fkeep prices low.
OL,26,@xD@ZOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779440815
OL,3,CCheaper tickets for summer attractions
OL,4,Cand kids meals as Reeves slashes VAT
OL,6,F"And today I am taking action by
OL,7,Fsuspending tariffs on over 100
OL,8,Fdifferent foods sold in supermarkets.
OL,10,F"And I am clear that I expect
OL,11,Fsupermarkets to pass these savings on
OL,12,Fin full to their customers."
OL,14,FShe added: "I will not tolerate any
OL,15,Fcompany exploiting the current
OL,16,Fsituation to make excess profits at
OL,17,Fconsumers' expense, so I am bringing
OL,18,Fforward tough new powers so that the
OL,19,FCompetition and Markets Authority and
OL,20,Fother regulators can take action when
OL,21,Ffirms break the rules."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUtD@\O]vD@LOU}D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
